OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FEngland take on Panama tonight as they
OL,7,Fseek to top their group in the World
OL,8,FCup, having already secured a place in
OL,9,Fthe knockout stages.
OL,11,FThe Three Lions go into their final
OL,12,Fgroup match in New Jersey on Saturday
OL,13,Fwith confidence, knowing progression
OL,14,Fis guaranteed, but top spot is still
OL,15,Fon the line.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
