OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782595102
OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FKick-off is at 10pm UK time, and fans
OL,7,Fwill be hoping for a repeat of the
OL,8,Fsides' last World Cup meeting in 2018,
OL,9,Fwhen England swept Panama aside with
OL,10,Fsix goals, including a hat-trick from
OL,11,Fcaptain Harry Kane.
OL,13,FMore than 15,000 England fans are
OL,14,Fexpected to travel to New Jersey for
OL,15,Fthe game.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
