OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FBack in the UK, the late kick-off time
OL,7,Fof 10pm is expected to spare
OL,8,Fsupporters from the daytime
OL,9,Ftemperatures of more than 30 C in
OL,10,Feast and south east England, as many
OL,11,Fare set to flock to pubs to watch the
OL,12,Fmatch.
OL,14,FThomas Tuchel's side will finish first
OL,15,Fin Group L if they can match Ghana's
OL,16,Fresult against Croatia, also on
OL,17,FSaturday, and likely face Senegal or
OL,18,FDR Congo, though that could change
OL,19,Fdepending on other results.
