OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FIf England were to finish second in
OL,7,Ftheir group, they would play the
OL,8,Fsecond-placed team in Group K, which
OL,9,Fis currently Portugal, in Toronto,
OL,10,FCanada, on Friday.
OL,12,FShould the Three Lions lose to Panama
OL,13,Fand finish third in the group, they
OL,14,Fwould play the winners of Group K,
OL,15,Fwhich is currently Colombia, next
OL,16,FSaturday, in Kansas City.
OL,18,FWho is in England's starting XI?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
