OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FTuchel has opted to rotate some
OL,7,Fplayers in Saturday's match due to the
OL,8,Finjury of the previous starting right-
OL,9,Fback, Reece James.
OL,11,FMorgan Rogers, Jarell Quansah, Bukayo
OL,12,FSaka and Marcus Rashford have all been
OL,13,Fbrought to the starting XI.
OL,15,FSaka has only been fit to come off the
OL,16,Fbench in England's first two games, as
OL,17,Fhe manages an Achilles injury which
OL,18,Faffected the latter part of his
OL,19,Fdomestic campaign with Arsenal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
