OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782595102
OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FTuchel has chosen to rest Declan Rice,
OL,7,Fwho was struggling with a calf issue
OL,8,Fpicked up during Tuesday's 0-0 draw
OL,9,Fwith Ghana.
OL,11,FThe vice-captain is also on a yellow
OL,12,Fcard so Tuchel decided to name him on
OL,13,Fthe bench, with Jude Bellingham
OL,14,Fdropping into the number eight
OL,15,Fposition and Rogers coming in at
OL,16,Fnumber 10.
OL,18,FSaturday's team:
OL,20,FGoalkeeper: Jordan Pickford
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
