OL,3,CEngland vs Panama: Three Lions aim to
OL,4,Cseal top spot in final group game
OL,6,FDefenders: Jarell Quansah, Marc Guehi,
OL,7,FEzri Konsa, Nico O'Reilly
OL,9,FMidfielders: Jude Bellingham, Elliot
OL,10,FAnderson.
OL,12,FAttackers: Bukayo Saka, Morgan Rogers,
OL,13,FMarcus Rashford, Harry Kane.
OL,15,FHow confident are England fans?
OL,17,FOn Friday, fans in New York said they
OL,18,Fbelieved Panama, who are at number 42
OL,19,Fin the Fifa rankings, would be no
OL,20,Fmatch for England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
